leadership_approach|vision_process_results_people|concentrated|vision|process|results|people|Recognised for Vision-first leadership|This leadership pattern shows up in how you set longer-range direction and future context before anything else. Others experience a clearer sense of direction, purpose, and future possibility.|At its best, Vision-first leadership gives people a longer-range direction to organise around. It narrows when that route is not enough, so bring Process, Results, or People in earlier when the situation needs stronger structure, clearer outcomes and next steps, or deeper shared confidence.|active|leadership_approach::vision_process_results_people::concentrated
leadership_approach|vision_process_results_people|paired|vision|process|results|people|Recognised for Vision-and-Process leadership|This leadership pattern shows up in how you combine setting longer-range direction and future context with organising the work into structure and sequence. Others experience a clearer sense of direction alongside a dependable path for getting the work done.|At its best, Vision-and-Process leadership combines longer-range direction with a reliable way of organising the work. It narrows when that pair runs ahead of Results or People, so bring them in earlier when the situation needs clearer outcomes and next steps or deeper shared confidence.|active|leadership_approach::vision_process_results_people::paired
